title: Duchess of Cambridge in labour with third child
text:
Duchess of Cambridge in labour with third child 10:05am BST - 00:45 
Kate, the wife of Prince William, is admitted to St. Mary's Hospital in London to give birth to the couple's third child and the latest member of Britain's royal family. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
